dct_title_s: Map of building lots situated in Chelsea belonging to the Ventnor Dredging Company and others
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Albany Terrace to Montpelier Avenue along the boardwalk in Atlantic City. Map depicts the numbered lots of land owned by the Ventnor Dredging Company. The West Jersey and Seashore Railroad and the Chelsea Branch Railroad are also shown.
